[[div class="skip_window" data-title="collected_accounts.zip"]]

Despite the fact that Miss Lapis went missing with the rest of the Amoni-Ram research team following the betrayal of Doctors Aram and Nussbaum, her documentation remained on the skipnet servers, with reports and updates being made in her name up to this day on the regular. The reason and mechanism behind this is unknown. 

Below you can find the collection of Miss Lapis' works. 

Since Miss Lapis has collaborated with many talented artists, curious people may turn to the Licensebox to find credit for every single illustration below. 

